      "description": "Generated when running-config differs from startup-config on a Cisco device, meaning unsaved changes will be lost on reload.\n\nParameters from DCI threshold context:\n   instance, instanceName - DCI instance\n   currentValue - \"No\" when configuration is unsaved\n   dciId, thresholdId - Standard threshold parameters",
      "severity": 1,
      "flags": 1,
      "message": "Unsaved configuration changes - running-config differs from startup-config; changes will be lost on reload",
      "tags": ""
    },
